  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/620340/extras/7be5dec4a01875ead26564622fbdddd4.avif?t=1547314855\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Cubrick is a 2D-platform puzzle game.<br><br>Players have to control 2 cubricks at the same time to solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/620340/extras/d563bf9207c7cd709f92d61eea83f9f1.avif?t=1547314855\" width=768 height=64 /></span><br><br>There are at least 50 levels and 5 secret levels.<br><br>Achievements and trading cards are available.<br><br>Play time around 2 hours.<br><br>Arrows to control; Enter to select; Esc to pause; Z to build.<br><br>And your brain to pass each level!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/620340/extras/69a13b9608311b59c46d962f03fa3e0b.avif?t=1547314855\" width=616 height=100 /></span>",
